tokens.name: Pøpe Døøm
tokens.description:
Was it he? Cardinal Dr Doomio? 
Who plotted this all along? 
But he is not a member 
Of the murderous and traitorous 
C Family… 
Perhaps just a beneficiary of a plot unbeknownst? Or was it he who planned this all… 
But he wasn't in the room when the knife was driven through Cardinal Clippius's back… 
…either way, he takes the throne, as the living cardinal with the most votes  

On June 2, 2025 we usher in:  

PØPE DØØM

tokens.name: The Murdered Pope Clippius
tokens.description:
It was plotted from the beginning 
The winner was always going to die 
Murdered 
By members of the CØNCLAVE 
The C Family conspired 
And he was slain by sword 
Lying dead in the chamber 
So pure, so helpful 
This token headby becomes 
A monument 
To Pøpe Clippius, the slain
